<td align="left" valign="bottom" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Stable Response</td>
<td align="left" valign="bottom" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Week 14 to<br>24</td>
<td align="left" valign="bottom" rowspan="1" colspan="1">50,000/µL</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left" valign="bottom" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Percentage of Participants Achieving 90% Improvement i (PASI90) at Week 16</td>
